research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Murchison City, TX, were identified primarily from the Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory. Bradley Gray is listed as the Mayor. The Council Members and their respective seats are also provided by the Texas Municipal League. While one agenda from October 2024 mentioned accepting the resignation of Torance McClean from the Murchison EDC, another agenda from the same month indicated his presence at a council meeting, and the Texas Municipal League directory still lists him as a Council Member. Therefore, he is included as a current council member.
